Use tool calls only. Step 1: Open Chrome browser and navigate to https://images.google.com. Step 2: Wait for page load then capture screen and run OCR. Step 3: Locate the search input box using OCR text match for "Search" or similar. Step 4: Use validate_click_target on the OCR-confirmed coordinates. Step 5: Click the search box only when valid=true and confidence Step 6: Type "dragonflies" via keyboard input. Step 7: Press Enter to submit. Step 8: Verify search results loaded via UI change detection.  
